15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 412, O.S.L.
16 2022 (69 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 4040), is amended to read as
17 follows:
18 Section 4040. A. There is hereby created until June 30, 2027,
19 the Oklahoma Route 66 Commission. The Commission shall be composed
20 of nine (9) members. The members shall serve as follows:
21 1. One member shall be appointed by the Governor and selected
22 from the Commissioners of the Oklahoma Tax Commission, whose first
23 term shall be for one (1) year, and then renewable for three-year
24 terms thereafter;
